<%- include("partials/public-shell-start", { pageTitle }) %>

<section class="hero-grid">
  <article class="panel panel-dark stack-lg">
    <span class="eyebrow">Help Center</span>
    <h2>Simple step-by-step guidance for voters and nomination applicants.</h2>
    <p>
      Use this page to understand exactly what to do before you vote or submit a nomination.
      The same instructions also help the election committee explain the process clearly to staff.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button" href="/help-center#vote-guide">How to Vote</a>
      <a class="button button-ghost" href="/help-center#nomination-guide">How to Apply for Nomination</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div>
        <strong>1</strong>
        <span>vote per staff member</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>1</strong>
        <span>application number per nomination</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>2</strong>
        <span>public self-service guides</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="panel panel-light stack-lg">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Quick Access</span>
        <h3>Open the right portal quickly.</h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid card-grid--compact">
      <article class="mini-card">
        <strong>Voters</strong>
        <p>Use your staff ID and phone number to enter the ballot when voting is open.</p>
        <a class="button button-ghost button-small" href="/vote/login">Open Voter Login</a>
      </article>

      <article class="mini-card">
        <strong>Nominees</strong>
        <p>Open the nomination form, complete every field, and save the application number after submitting.</p>
        <a class="button button-ghost button-small" href="/nomination/form">Open Nomination Form</a>
      </article>

      <article class="mini-card">
        <strong>Status Check</strong>
        <p>Already submitted a nomination? Use your application number to check the current committee decision.</p>
        <a class="button button-ghost button-small" href="/nomination/status/login">Check Status</a>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="note-block">
      <strong>Tip:</strong> You can share this page with staff so they see both processes in one place before election day.
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="split-stage">
  <article class="panel panel-light stack-lg" id="vote-guide">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Voting Guide</span>
        <h3>How voters cast their vote</h3>
      </div>
      <a class="button button-ghost button-small" href="/vote/login">Go to Voting Portal</a>
    </div>

    <ol class="flow-list">
      <li>Open the voter portal from the home page or go directly to the voter login page.</li>
      <li>Enter your registered staff ID and phone number exactly as they were loaded into the system.</li>
      <li>If voting is open, the system verifies your details and lets you enter the ballot.</li>
      <li>Choose one candidate for a position, or skip that position if you do not want to vote there.</li>
      <li>Click next to move through the remaining positions one by one.</li>
      <li>Review your selections on the confirmation screen before final submission.</li>
      <li>Submit your ballot once. After submission, you cannot vote again or edit the vote.</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="feature-grid guide-feature-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h4>Before you start</h4>
        <p>Make sure the election window is open and your phone number matches the one registered for your staff ID.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h4>During voting</h4>
        <p>Read each position carefully and move step by step until you reach the review screen.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h4>After submission</h4>
        <p>The system marks you as voted immediately, so you cannot log in again to cast another ballot.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="panel panel-light stack-lg" id="nomination-guide">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Nomination Guide</span>
        <h3>How nominees apply for a position</h3>
      </div>
      <a class="button button-ghost button-small" href="/nomination/form">Open Nomination Form</a>
    </div>

    <ol class="flow-list">
      <li>Open the nomination form from the election home page.</li>
      <li>If the nomination period has not started yet, you will see the form and countdown but submission stays locked until the opening time.</li>
      <li>Fill in your full name, department, staff ID, phone number, and the position you want to contest.</li>
      <li>Upload your candidate photo and complete your short profile, manifesto, proposer name, and seconder name.</li>
      <li>Tick the declaration checkbox and submit the form once the nomination window is open.</li>
      <li>After successful submission, save the application number shown by the system.</li>
      <li>Use that application number later to check your nomination status, download your filled form, or continue any correction requested by the committee.</li>
    </ol>

    <div class="feature-grid guide-feature-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h4>Important timing</h4>
        <p>Nominations close automatically when voting starts, so applicants should submit before the election opens.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h4>Application number</h4>
        <p>Every successful nomination gets a unique application number. Keep it safely because it is required for status checking.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h4>Committee review</h4>
        <p>The committee can approve, reject, or request correction before a nominee is published as a candidate.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="panel panel-light stack-lg">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Need More Help</span>
      <h3>Use the portal tools below.</h3>
    </div>
    <p>These links take staff directly into the correct workflow.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="button-row">
    <a class="button" href="/vote/login">Open Voter Login</a>
    <a class="button button-ghost" href="/nomination/form">Open Nomination Form</a>
    <a class="button button-ghost" href="/nomination/status/login">Check Nomination Status</a>
    <a class="button button-ghost" href="/downloads/organization-vote-portal-user-guide.pdf">Download User Guide PDF</a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include("partials/public-shell-end") %>
